{
  "stem": "23090.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And said let-- well, I'm sure she's telling them the truth and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Since she was not married, so there would be no reason for her to have family or this-- or, you know, children and that and so on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they just did a very quick search and went on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were able to be there another few days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the scheme of things, it-- it didn't turn out as a permanent solution.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was a few more days of being in the ghetto and hiding.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the ultimate result would have been, if we'd gone earlier, it would be the same place as we wound up at the-- at the end.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Do you know why your parents chose to leave the place of hiding?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they were-- there was-- there was no one else there anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you cannot get food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You cannot do anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once-- once-- once you evacuate an area, there's nothing that's supposed to move.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A dog, a cat, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because that's supposed to be a dead, total, complete, silent area.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you can't sit there for weeks or months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no way of getting food anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no way of communicating with anything other than dying in the-- in the attic.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So ultimately, you just succumbed to the fact that you're going to go to the next place and hoping that you can survive and-- and-- and move along.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There, it was sure death, because there was nowhere else to receive anything in terms of food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this is the reason we-- we continued on that journey and-- and going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we were gathered, and-- and we-- we were basically already packed and everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
